@Node Intro "AmTAGID3 / Introduction"

@{_Section "AmTAGID3"}

  @{b}@{u}AmTAGID3@{uu}@{ub} is a useful program to edit the @{" TAG ID3 " link TAGID3} part of a @{" MPEG Audio " link MPEGAudio}
  file, with features as follows :

  @{b} · @{ub}  Read the TAG ID3 info from any MPEG Audio file.

  @{b} · @{ub}  @{" Write " Link Write} the TAG ID3 info to any MPEG Audio file.

  @{b} · @{ub}  @{" Wipe " Link Wipe} the TAG ID3 info of any MPEG Audio file.

  @{b} · @{ub}  @{" Displays " Link MP3Duration} the duration of the MPEG Audio file.

  @{b} · @{ub}  @{" Show & edit " Link ADOSComment} the AmigaDOS comment of the MPEG Audio file.

  @{b} · @{ub}  Press « Help » over the gadgets to get context sensitive online help.

  @{b}AmTAGID3@{ub} is Shell only but this was intended from the start :)

  This programs is @{B}NOT@{UB} FreeWare... It's @{B}@{U}EMailWare@{UB}@{UU} and/or @{B}@{U}PostCardWare@{UB}@{UU}.  This
  means that if you like and use this program, you have the moral obligation
  to send an @{U}EMail@{UU} and/or a @{U}PostCard@{UU} (your country,  city,  etc...)  to  the
  @{" author " link author} :-)

@EndNode

